data.description: **BACK ON THE MARKET - MOTIVATED SELLERS! All offers being considered *** This Spectacular one level spacious floor Plan offers 4 Bedrooms with new luxury vinyl wood flooring throughout all bedrooms, 2.5 Bathrooms, and a 3 Car Garage with almost 2300 heated Square Feet, and fresh new paint throughout the home. This home features a bright and wide open floor plan with volume ceilings. The kitchen features granite countertops, with a beautiful backsplash, a breakfast bar/island, and large pantry. The oversized master suite includes a large walk-in closet; dual vanity sinks, and a spacious garden tub with a separate walk-in shower. This M/I built home is located in the lovely neighborhood of Ridge Crest Community in the Dover/North Brandon area and offers both the tranquility of an "off the beat path" neighborhood and the benefit of being in the heart of it all. Tucked away off Valrico Road near Brandon Blvd, this home provides easy access to I75, I4, Brandon Mall, Brandon Hospital and all of the dining and entertainment the Brandon area has to offer. This welcoming neighborhood features beautiful curb appeal, a park for small events, and once inside your home, the open floor plan makes a great layout for entertainment. Call today for your private showing!
